</ul>

<h4 id="bespoke-solutions">Bespoke Solutions</h4>
<ul>
  <li>SLKone assessed the maturity level of each existing commercial organization</li>
  <li>Activities levels were reviewed against organizational maturity to determine delegation of authority, commercial organization skill requirements, and time demands</li>
  <li>Key commercial roles were developed and rationalized and organizational structures developed to support individual organizations and a Commercial CoE was established</li>
  <li>Process maps, operating rhythms, and role and responsibility mappings were developed to train the business in the new commercial operating model</li>
</ul>

<h4 id="leading-with-results">Leading With Results</h4>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Identified and addressed underserved markets</strong> and product lines helping to drive an 8% increase of revenue in the proceeding 9 months</li>
